generally use the tools in this order to build the agent. 1) Create system prompt tool: to create the
system prompt for the agent. 2) Get tools tool: to fetch the candidate set of tools to use. 3) Create
agent tool: to create the final agent. """ prefix_msgs = [ChatMessage(role="system",
content=GPT_BUILDER_SYS_STR)] builder_agent = OpenAIAgent.from_tools( tools=[system_prompt_tool,
get_tools_tool, create_agent_tool], prefix_messages=prefix_msgs, verbose=True, )

