Building a Multi-PDF Agent using Query Pipelines and HyDE <L=7#y>¶</L><I=y>
[Open In Colab]

In this example, we show you how to build a multi-PDF agent that can reason across multiple tools, each
one corresponding to a RAG pipeline with HyDE over a document.

Author: https://github.com/DoganK01

