verbose=True, with_main_worker=False ): """Helper function for building introspective agent using
tool-interactive reflection. Steps: 1. Define the `ToolInteractiveReflectionAgentWorker` 1a. Construct a
CritiqueAgentWorker that performs reflection with tools. 1b. Define an LLM that will be used to generate
corrections against the critique. 1c. Define a function that determines the stopping condition for
