Try out LLMCompiler for RAG <L=k#Z>¶</L><I=Z>
Now let's try out the LLMCompiler for RAG use cases. Specifically, we load a dataset of Wikipedia
articles about various cities and ask questions over them.

Setup Data <L=k#10>¶</L><I=10>
We use our  WikipediaReader  to load data for various cities.

