Action: add
Action Input: {'a': 20, 'b': 8}
Observation: 28
> Running step 73464ecd-b266-47ef-8f1b-c0aa0e43ad60. Step input: None
Thought: I have now calculated the entire expression 20+(2*4) and have the final result.
Answer: 28
```

