tools=query_engine_tools, query="How has the total amount of San Francisco's budget changed from 2016 to
2023?", ) print(result)

Our debug output is lengthy! You can see the sub-questions being generated and then  sub_question() 
being repeatedly invoked, each time generating a brief log of ReAct agent thoughts and actions to answer
each smaller question.

You can see  combine_answers  running multiple times; these were triggered by each  AnswerEvent  but
before all 8  AnswerEvents  were collected. On its final run it generates a full prompt, combines the
answers and returns the result.
