OpenAI Agent Workarounds for Lengthy Tool Descriptions <L=v#M>¶</L><I=M>
In this demo, we illustrate a workaround for defining an OpenAI tool whose description exceeds OpenAI's
current limit of 1024 characters. For simplicity, we will build upon the  QueryPlanTool  notebook
example.

If you're opening this Notebook on colab, you will probably need to install LlamaIndex 🦙.

