Assistant Agent with your own Vector Store / Retrieval API <L=C#1a>¶</L><I=1a>
LlamaIndex has 35+ vector database integrations. Instead of using the in-house Retrieval API, you can use
our assistant agent over any vector store.

Here is our full list of vector store integrations . We picked one vector store (Supabase) using a random
number generator.

