agent = OpenAIAssistantAgent.from_new(
    name="QA bot",
    instructions="You are a bot designed to answer questions about the author",
    openai_tools=[],
    tools=[summary_tool, vector_tool],
    verbose=True,
    run_retrieve_sleep_time=1.0,
)
```

