Benchmarking OpenAI Retrieval API (through Assistant Agent) <L=F#12>¶</L><I=12>
[Open In Colab]

This guide benchmarks the Retrieval Tool from the OpenAI Assistant API , by using our
 OpenAIAssistantAgent  . We run over the Llama 2 paper, and compare generation quality against a naive
RAG pipeline.

