ReAct Agent - A Simple Intro with Calculator Tools <L=G#I>¶</L><I=I>
This is a notebook that showcases the ReAct agent over very simple calculator tools (no fancy RAG
pipelines or API calls).

We show how it can reason step-by-step over different tools to achieve the end goal.

If you're opening this Notebook on colab, you will probably need to install LlamaIndex 🦙.

