Load Data <L=T#n>¶</L><I=n>
We will use a sample news article dataset retrieved from Diffbot, which Tomaz has conveniently made
available on GitHub for easy access.

The dataset contains 2,500 samples; for ease of experimentation, we will use 50 of these samples, which
include the  title  and  text  of news articles.

