Full-Stack Web Application <L=1y#1>#</L><I=1>
LlamaIndex can be integrated into a downstream full-stack web application. It can be used in a backend
server (such as Flask), packaged into a Docker container, and/or directly used in a framework such as
Streamlit.

We provide tutorials and resources to help you get started in this area:

- Fullstack Application Guide shows you how to build an app with LlamaIndex as an API and a
  TypeScript+React frontend
- Fullstack Application with Delphic walks you through using LlamaIndex with a production-ready web app
  starter template called Delphic.
- The LlamaIndex Starter Pack provides very basic flask, streamlit, and docker examples for LlamaIndex.
</B>
